# Test Data Utility Style

- Keep a single static fixture utility class with private constructor.
- Provide focused factory methods (`createTestXxxA/B`) returning fully built entities.
- Build fixtures with entity builders to keep defaults explicit and readable.
- Keep values deterministic and simple to support stable integration assertions.
